'''斯蒂芬·迈克尔·格利森'''（{{lang-en|Stephen Michael Gleeson}}；{{bd|1988年|8月3日}}）<ref name="Hugman2010-11 169">{{Cite book |editor=Hugman, Barry J. |title=The PFA Footballers' Who's Who 2010–11 |date=2010 |publisher=Mainstream |isbn=978-1-84596-601-0 |page=169}}</ref>是一位[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]足球運動員，在場上的位置是中場。他現在效力於英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽球隊[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|伊普斯维奇]]。他亦曾代表愛爾蘭國家足球隊參賽。

==球會生涯==
格利森生於[[都柏林|都柏林]]<ref name="Hugman2010-11 169">{{Cite book |editor=Hugman, Barry J. |title=The PFA Footballers' Who's Who 2010–11 |date=2010 |publisher=Mainstream |isbn=978-1-84596-601-0 |page=169}}</ref>，曾效力家鄉球會[[车历奥察德足球會|车历奥察德]]，在2006年5月獲得[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]提供的三年合約，便赴英格蘭發展<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/4755027.stm |title=Gleeson signs Wolves pro contract |publisher=BBC Sport |date=9 May 2006 |accessdate=17 July 2014 |archive-date=2007-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070312073352/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/4755027.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2006/07賽季他被外借至[[英乙|英乙]][[斯托克港足球俱乐部|斯托克港]]三個月，在2006年11月11日的[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]對[[埃克塞特城足球俱乐部|埃克塞特城]]時首次上場。回到狼隊後，獲得四次替補上場機會，包括在晉級附加賽半決賽第二輪不敵[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布罗姆维奇]]。新賽季格利森只在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]上場一次而已<ref name=sb0708>{{cite web |title=Games played by Stephen Gleeson in 2007/2008 |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=45301&season_id=137 |work=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=17 July 2014 |archive-date=2015-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705233142/http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=45301&season_id=137 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。為了獲得更多比賽機會，2008年2月21日外借至[[靴尔福特联足球俱乐部|靴尔福特联]]一個月<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/hereford_united/7256714.stm |title=Hereford bring in Gleeson on loan |publisher=BBC Sport |date=21 February 2008 |accessdate=2015-07-04 |archive-date=2008-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080225155121/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/hereford_united/7256714.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。外借結束後，不到數天又被外借到斯托克港，租借期至季末。在晉級附加賽準決賽對[[韦康比流浪者足球俱乐部|韦康比流浪者]]時取得進球，助球隊殺進決賽，該進球後來被球迷選為「2008年最佳進球<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stockportcounty.com/page/LatestNews/0,,10419~1522996,00.html |title=Goal of 2008 |publisher=Stockport County F.C. |date=16 January 2009 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723102604/http://www.stockportcounty.com/page/LatestNews/0%2C%2C10419~1522996%2C00.html |archivedate=2011-07-23|deadurl=yes }}</ref>」。格利森在晉級附加賽決賽上場並助球隊成功晉級至[[英甲|英甲]]<ref name=sb0708/>。

2008/09賽季，格利森有一半時間都效力斯托克港<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stockport/7550119.stm |title=Hatters bring in Gleeson on loan |publisher=BBC Sport |date=8 August 2008 |accessdate=17 July 2014}}</ref>。租借完結後在2009年3月再被母會外借，這次是英甲球會[[米尔顿凯恩斯足球俱乐部|米尔顿凯恩斯]]，租借期至賽季完結<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/m/milton_keynes_dons/7964395.stm |title=MK Dons snap up Wolves midfielder |publisher=BBC Sport |date=25 March 2009 |accessdate=17 July 2014 |archive-date=2018-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180515113548/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/m/milton_keynes_dons/7964395.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===米尔顿凯恩斯===
2009年7月1日，格利森永久加盟米尔顿凯恩斯，雙方簽約三年，轉會費不對外公佈<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wolves.co.uk/page/News/0,,10307~1710098,00.html |title=Gleeson Joins MK Dons |publisher=Wolverhampton Wanderers |date=1 July 2009 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090929124002/http://www.wolves.co.uk/page/News/0%2C%2C10307~1710098%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-09-29|deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2011年1月25日，他的{{convert|30|yd}}漂亮遠射攻破[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|莱顿东方]]球門打開紀錄，最後以2-2戰平<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/9369742.stm |publisher=BBC Sport |title=Leyton Orient 2–2 MK Dons |date=25 January 2011 |accessdate=17 July 2014}}</ref>。2012年12月2日的足總盃他又打進類似的球，使球隊以2-1擊敗[[AFC溫布頓|AFC溫布頓]]晉級<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2012/dec/02/mk-dons-afc-wimbledon-match-report |title=MK Dons defeat AFC Wimbledon in the FA Cup with late Jon Otsemobor goal |first=Paul |last=Doyle |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2 December 2012 |accessdate=17 July 2014 |archive-date=2015-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706034611/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2012/dec/02/mk-dons-afc-wimbledon-match-report |dead-url=no }}</ref>。數週後他在訓練期間左腳受傷，需要休養至2013年3月5日對[[唐卡斯特流浪足球俱乐部|唐卡斯特流浪]]的比賽才能上場。他在該場比賽打進一球，以3-0輕取對方<ref>{{cite web |title=Karl: Near-perfect |url=http://www.mkdons.com/news/article/karl-near-perfect-696415.aspx |publisher=Milton Keynes Dons F.C. |date=5 March 2013 |accessdate=6 March 2013 |archive-date=2015-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705162224/http://www.mkdons.com/news/article/karl-near-perfect-696415.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年4月的數場比賽，由於隊長[[迪安·莱温顿|迪安·莱温顿]]受傷缺陣，格利森成為了球隊隊長並在對[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|布伦特福德]]賽事未段攻進一球，助球隊取得兩連勝<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.miltonkeynes.co.uk/sport/football/mk-dons/dons-just-have-to-keep-winning-says-gleeson-1-4956388 |title=Dons just have to keep winning says Gleeson |newspaper=Milton Keynes Citizen |date=2 April 2013 |accessdate=17 July 2014 |archive-date=2018-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180701165239/https://www.miltonkeynes.co.uk/sport/football/mk-dons/dons-just-have-to-keep-winning-says-gleeson-1-4956388 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。可是對[[斯温登足球俱乐部|斯温登]]期間中場因傷被換出，最終球隊以2-0勝出<ref>{{cite web |title=MK Dons 2–0 Swindon |url=http://www.mkdons.com/fixtures-results/match-report/index.aspx?matchid=3595182&pageView=full |publisher=Milton Keynes Dons F.C. |date=9 April 2013 |accessdate=17 July 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140725192519/http://www.mkdons.com/fixtures-results/match-report/index.aspx?matchid=3595182&pageView=full |archivedate=2014年7月25日 }}</ref>。

===伯明翰城===
格利森在2014年夏天自由轉會至英冠球隊伯明翰城，簽約兩年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20140605-official-blues-bag-irish-midfielder-1612403.aspx |title=Official: Birmingham City sign Irish midfielder |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=9 June 2014 |accessdate=17 July 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114553/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20140605-official-blues-bag-irish-midfielder-1612403.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在球季揭幕日首次代表球隊上場對戰[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米德尔斯堡]]，以2-0戰敗完場<ref name=sb1314>{{cite web |title=Games played by Stephen Gleeson in 2013/2014 |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=45301&season_id=143 |work=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=17 July 2014 |archive-date=2015-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706004501/http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=45301&season_id=143 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
格利森在2007年8月首次代表愛爾蘭U21參賽對戰[[德國21歲以下國家足球隊|德國U21]]，首次上場便打進兩球，戰果為2-2。在2007年5月23日對[[厄瓜多爾國家足球隊|厄瓜多爾]]的友誼賽首次為國上場，地點為美國[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]的[[巨人球場|巨人球場]]，最終以1-1戰平。

